## Operating Rule

Every ninth-wave post needs a status label. Use `SOURCE_LEAD` for captured papers, `PROBE_MATCH` only for bounded triage observations, and `UNVERIFIABLE` for paper-readiness claims until claims, methods, negative controls, and recheck commands exist.
